Multivariate Derivatives
Non-Separable
\[f(x,y) = x^{2} \cdot y^{1/2}\]



Partial w.r.t. \(x\)


\[\begin{align*}
\dfrac{df}{dx} &= 2x^{2-1} \cdot y^{1/2} \\
&= 2xy^{1/2}
\end{align*}\]



Partial w.r.t. \(y\)


\[\begin{align*}
\dfrac{df}{dy} &= \dfrac{1}{2}y^{1/2 - 1} \cdot x^{2} \\
&= \dfrac{1}{2} \cdot \dfrac{1}{y^{1/2}} \cdot x^{2}
\end{align*}\]

