“New” Supply Curve
The Supply Curve will follow:
\[\begin{equation*}
\text{Supply Curve} =
    \begin{cases}
        P = MC(Q^{*}) &\text{if} \;\;\; P \geq \min\{AVC(Q^{*})\} \\ \\
        Q = 0 &\text{if} \;\;\;  P &lt; \min\{AVC(Q^{*})\}
    \end{cases}
\end{equation*}\]

